<HEADLINE> India's Aggressive Act, Serious Threat to S. Asian Peace: Pak Minister </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, August 11 (Xinhua) -- Pakistan's Information
Minister Mushahid Hussain said Wednesday that India's aggressive
act by shooting down an unarmed Pakistan Navy aircraft is a
serious threat to peace, security and stability in South Asia.
</P>
