<HEADLINE> ADB Provides Health Loan to Marshall Islands </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, August 12 (Xinhua) -- The Asian Development Bank (ADB)
approved Thursday a 9.25-million-U.S.-dollar loan to the Republic
of the Marshall Islands for various health and infrastructure
works in its Ebeye islet.
</P>
