Lee Teng-hui takes no heed of their security, interests, or well
being, and his attempt will lead to calamities for the 22 million
Taiwan people as well.
</P>
<P>
The article concluded that no matter how the written
explanation tries to exonerate Lee Teng-hui from responsibility,
Lee is the "trouble maker" of the international community.
