the Central Government, go to the State Council." He also asked
that more people be drawn to Beijing. "The more, the better," he
said, stressing that "this will be the last chance."
</P>
<P>
At this secret meeting, Li worked out a strategy for the
massing around the Zhongnanhai. The gathering could not be
accomplished in the name of the Research Society of Falun Dafa and
its branches, and ordinary practitioners should be pushed to the
front line.
</P>
