the expansion of bilateral cooperation in various fields, and said
he hopes contact on different levels will increase so as to
explore new cooperative channels.
</P>
<P>
As to economic and trade cooperation, he said, both sides
should fully tap their respective advantages and seek economic
complementarity, Zhu said.
</P>
