<HEADLINE> Military Expert: Splitting of Motherland is Invitation of Destruction </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 12 (Xinhua) -- A military strategist has said
that Lee Teng-hui's separatist principle violates the basic
interests of the Chinese nation and invites destruction.
</P>
<P>
Peng Guangqian of the strategy research department of the
Chinese Academy of Military Sciences said Lee Teng-hui is in fact
an abnormal "test-tube baby" bred by international anti-China
forces in their political lab.
</P>
<P>
He said Lee's separatist principle seriously threatens Taiwan's
political future, the reunification of the Chinese nation, and
peace and stability in the Asia-Pacific Region.
</P>
<P>
He emphasized that Lee's separatist statement is a major
provocation to 1.2 billion Chinese, including 21 million Taiwan
people.
</P>
<P>
He said the Chinese people obtained national independence by
unyielding and arduous struggle, and many devoted their lives to
this great undertaking.
</P>
<P>
He emphasized that China will never allow any separatist acts
to prevail.
</P>
<P>
Peng said Taiwan is the marine shield for safeguarding the
security of the mainland areas, and is also the strategic hub for
controlling the western Pacific.
</P>
<P>
He said the situation in Taiwan and the Taiwan Straits concerns
the security and development of the Chinese nation.
</P>
<P>
China will never allow separatist plots to hinder the mainland
areas' economic development or destroy the undertaking of
reunification, Peng concluded. 
</P>
</TEXT>
